            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the beef is browning, peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Slice <strong>half </strong>your <strong>red chilli[es]</strong> into rounds and finely chop the rest</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1673867326964-x200.jpg",
