        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Thai-style sticky chilli beef</strong> over the <strong>fragrant</strong> <strong>rice salad</strong>, topped with the <strong>chopped coriander</strong>, <strong>mint leaves</strong> and your <strong>crispy onions</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>reserved chilli rounds</strong> (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)<strong> </strong>and a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
